  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EEFGroupStyle, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EStructuralFeature.Internal.DynamicValueHolder, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.InternalEObject

    public class EEFGroupStyleImpl
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.impl.MinimalEObjectImpl.Container
implements EEFGroupStyle
    An implementation of the model object 'EEF Group Style'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Background Color Expression
    • Foreground Color Expression
    • Font Name Expression
    • Font Size Expression
    • Bar Style
    • Toggle Style
    • Expanded By Default
